{{more citations needed|date=December 2012}}
The '''Advanced Radar Research Center''' ('''ARRC''') is a University Strategic Organization{{clarify|date=December 2012}} of the [[University of Oklahoma]] (OU) located at the Radar Innovation Lab (RIL) in [[Norman, Oklahoma]].<ref>https://www.unidata.ucar.edu/blogs/news/entry/university_of_oklahoma_director_advanced</ref> The Executive Director of ARRC is Dr. Robert D. Palmer.

