'''Natural Sciences Museum of [[Albania]]''' is a [[natural science]] museum in [[Tirana]], [[Albania]] and was established in 1948. The museum is affiliated with the [[University of Tirana]] and has branches in [[zoology]], [[botany]] and [[geology]].<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CKtuz7SJJagC&pg=PA44&dq=National+Archaeological+Museum+tirana&hl=en&ei=O-NOTOLyFMrZ4wbA75yACA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CDsQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=National%20Archaeological%20Museum%20tirana&f=false|title=The World of Learning 2004|publisher=[[Europa Publications]], [[Routledge]]|author=Salzman, Michael|edition=54|page=44|year=2003|isbn=1-85743-182-0}}</ref>

